'''Robot Kyle''' is a legacy [[Avatars|avatar]], part of the list of VRChat's [[Public Avatars|public avatars]]. Robot Kyle was once VRChat's default avatar{{citation needed}}, before [[VRChat]] created their own [[Robot]] avatar.

==Origin==
Robot Kyle was created by Kyle Brewer, and later released under Unity Technologies<ref>[https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/3d/characters/robots/robot-kyle-urp-4696 Robot Kyle | URP] on ''Unity Asset Store''; retrieved December 20, 2024.</ref>. The model was made public during the release of Unity 4.0 on October 15, 2012. VRChat uploaded a cross-platform version of the avatar on May 11, 2019. Previous versions of this avatar, by VRChat, existed prior to the 2019 cross-platform release of Robot Kyle, but has since been deleted. 

